# LiveKit Golden Image Build Runbook

## Purpose

Create a standardized Ubuntu Golden Image for:

* LiveKit Server
* LiveKit SIP
* Voice AI Agents
* Redis Services
* Docker Workloads

Target Compliance:

* CIS Benchmark Level 1
* Production Ready
* Cloud Deployable
* Reusable Across Environments

---

# Phase 1: Base Operating System

## Supported OS

Preferred:

* Ubuntu Server 24.04 LTS

Fallback:

* Ubuntu Server 22.04 LTS

---

# Phase 2: Initial Server Validation

Verify:

```bash
cat /etc/os-release
uname -r
hostnamectl
```

Check Resources:

```bash
lscpu
free -h
df -h
```

Check Networking:

```bash
ip addr
ip route
ss -tulpn
```

---

# Phase 3: System Update

```bash
apt update
apt upgrade -y
apt autoremove -y
```

Reboot if kernel updated.

---

# Phase 4: Install Base Packages

```bash
apt install -y \
curl \
wget \
git \
vim \
jq \
unzip \
net-tools \
htop \
chrony \
rsyslog \
software-properties-common
```

---

# Phase 5: Configure Time Synchronization

```bash
systemctl enable chrony
systemctl start chrony
chronyc tracking
```

---

# Phase 6: Docker Installation

```bash
curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com | bash
```

Enable:

```bash
systemctl enable docker
systemctl start docker
```

Verify:

```bash
docker version
```

---

# Phase 7: Docker Hardening

Create:

```bash
mkdir -p /etc/docker
```

File:

```bash
nano /etc/docker/daemon.json
```

Content:

```json
{
  "live-restore": true,
  "log-driver": "json-file",
  "log-opts": {
    "max-size": "100m",
    "max-file": "10"
  }
}
```

Restart:

```bash
systemctl restart docker
```

---

# Phase 8: SSH Hardening

Edit:

```bash
nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config
```

Configure:

```ini
PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication no
PubkeyAuthentication yes
MaxAuthTries 3
ClientAliveInterval 300
ClientAliveCountMax 2
```

Validate:

```bash
sshd -t
```

Restart:

```bash
systemctl restart ssh
```

---

# Phase 9: Firewall Configuration

Install:

```bash
apt install ufw -y
```

Configure:

```bash
ufw default deny incoming
ufw default allow outgoing

ufw allow 22/tcp
ufw allow 80/tcp
ufw allow 443/tcp
ufw allow 7880/tcp
ufw allow 5349/tcp
ufw allow 50000:60000/udp

ufw enable
```

Verify:

```bash
ufw status verbose
```

---

# Phase 10: Fail2Ban

Install:

```bash
apt install fail2ban -y
```

Enable:

```bash
systemctl enable fail2ban
```

Create:

```bash
nano /etc/fail2ban/jail.local
```

Content:

```ini
[sshd]
enabled=true
maxretry=3
findtime=600
bantime=3600
```

Restart:

```bash
systemctl restart fail2ban
```

Verify:

```bash
fail2ban-client status
```

---

# Phase 11: Auditd

Install:

```bash
apt install auditd audispd-plugins -y
```

Enable:

```bash
systemctl enable auditd
systemctl start auditd
```

Verify:

```bash
auditctl -s
```

---

# Phase 12: Automatic Security Updates

Install:

```bash
apt install unattended-upgrades -y
```

Enable:

```bash
dpkg-reconfigure unattended-upgrades
```

Verify:

```bash
systemctl status unattended-upgrades
```

---

# Phase 13: Kernel Hardening

Create:

```bash
nano /etc/sysctl.d/99-security.conf
```

Add:

```ini
net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1
net.ipv4.conf.all.accept_redirects=0
net.ipv4.conf.default.accept_redirects=0
net.ipv4.conf.all.send_redirects=0
net.ipv4.conf.default.send_redirects=0
net.ipv4.conf.all.rp_filter=1
kernel.randomize_va_space=2
```

Apply:

```bash
sysctl --system
```

---

# Phase 14: Monitoring

Install Node Exporter:

```bash
apt install prometheus-node-exporter -y
```

Enable:

```bash
systemctl enable prometheus-node-exporter
```

Install Fluent Bit (Optional):

```bash
apt install fluent-bit -y
```

---

# Phase 15: CIS Benchmark Validation

Install Lynis:

```bash
apt install lynis -y
```

Run:

```bash
lynis audit system
```

Target:

```text
Hardening Index > 80
```

Store Reports:

```bash
cp /var/log/lynis.log /root/
cp /var/log/lynis-report.dat /root/
```

---

# Phase 16: LiveKit Prerequisites

Required Ports:

```text
22/tcp
80/tcp
443/tcp
7880/tcp
5349/tcp
50000-60000/udp
```

Required Services:

```text
Docker
Chrony
SSH
UFW
Fail2Ban
Auditd
```

---

# Phase 17: Pre-Golden Image Cleanup

Remove Temporary Data:

```bash
apt autoremove -y
apt clean
```

Clean Logs:

```bash
truncate -s 0 /var/log/*.log
```

Clear History:

```bash
history -c
```

Cloud Init Cleanup:

```bash
cloud-init clean
```

Remove Secrets:

```text
SSH Host Keys
TLS Certificates
API Keys
OpenAI Keys
Deepgram Keys
Redis Passwords
LiveKit Secrets
```

---

# Phase 18: Golden Image Validation

Verify:

```bash
docker version
ufw status
fail2ban-client status
auditctl -s
chronyc tracking
lynis audit system
```

Expected Result:

* CIS Level 1 Compliant
* Docker Ready
* LiveKit Ready
* Security Hardened
* Monitoring Enabled
* Cloud Deployable

---

